)

Description
The function is used to parse chirp/profile configurations and save configuration and derived parameter in datapath parameter structure.

Parameters
[out]outParamsPointer to parameters generated after parsing configuration
[in]subFrameIdxSub-frame index
[in]openCfgPointer to the MMWave Open configuration
[in]ctrlCfgPointer to the MMWave Control configuration
[in]adcBufCfgPointer to ADCBuf configuration
[in]rfFreqScaleFactorRF frequency scale factor, see SOC_getDeviceRFFreqScaleFactor API
Return values
Success- = 0
Error- < 0, one of RF Parser Error Codes
